ent/uploads/2021/11/black-friday-buying-guide.jpg 1120w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 744px) 100vw, 744px\" />\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-technology\">Technology</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-software\">Software</h3>\n\n\n\n<h4><a href=\"https://app.convertkit.com/referrals/l/b1d59b32-c23a-48d2-9db7-47994d28a882\">ConvertKit</a> — Starting at $0/mo</h4>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<p>If you’re on our newsletter (and if not you should be <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/13.1.0/72x72/1f447.png\" alt=\"?\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" />) you’ve already seen ConvertKit. It’s a fantastic email marketing tool that has powerful and visual automation features.</p>\n\n\n<noscript class=\"ninja-forms-noscript-message\">\n    Notice: JavaScript is required for this content.</noscript><style>\n\n        /* FORM STYLES */\n    \n        #nf-form-45-cont {\n                                    background-color:#f1f1f1;\n                                            padding:15px;\n                    }\n    </style><div id=\"nf-form-45-cont\" class=\"nf-form-cont\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-labelledby=\"nf-form-title-45\" aria-describedby=\"nf-form-errors-45\" role=\"form\">\n\n    <div class=\"nf-loading-spinner\"></div>\n\n</div>\n        <!-- TODO: Move to Template File. -->\n        <script>var formDisplay=1;var nfForms=nfForms||[];var form=[];form.id=\'45\';form.settings={\"objectType\":\"Form Setting\",\"editActive\":true,\"title\":\"ConvertKit List Subscribe\",\"show_title\":0,\"allow_public_link\":0,\"embed_form\":\"\",\"clear_complete\":1,\"hide_complete\":1,\"default_label_pos\":\"hidden\",\"wrapper_class\":\"\",\"element_class\":\"\",\"key\":\"\",\"add_submit\":0,\"changeEmailErrorMsg\":\"Please enter a valid email address!\",\"changeDateErrorMsg\":\"Please enter a valid date!\",\"confirmFieldErrorMsg\":\"These fields must match!\",\"fieldNumberNumMinError\":\"Number Min Error\",\