ing -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> “<strong>we</strong>”, “<strong>us</strong>” or “<strong>our</strong>” refers to ??????????</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>“<strong>you</strong>” and “<strong>your</strong>” refers to every person that accesses our website also referred to as a user.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>“<strong>registered user(s)</strong>” refers to a registered user with unique credentials for the purpose of acquiring goods and services.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Legal Age</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you are below the age of 18 years, permission from a parent or guardian is required.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We may verify such permission, by asking you to provide us with contact details. We may also check that the contact details you have given us are correct and are the details of a person who is actually your parent or guardian. If we are not able to verify such permission you may not use our service.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We reserver the right to refuse selling certain products to you if you are under the age of 18 regardless of parent or guardian permission.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>You may be requested to provide proof of your age before being able to buy certain products</strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Accuracy of Information</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We processes data in a manner that is reasonable, adequate, relevant, non-excessive and purpose-specific. In order to use our service we collect and process Personal Information. When you register as a user, we have to collect and process your data in order to render our services to you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When you register to use our service, we may collect information such as your name and surname, email address, physical address, gender, mobile phone number, online identifiers, date of birth, national identification or passport number.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Should your data change or you wish to correct your Personal Information you can do this by updating your account profile.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You hereby warrant that information you provide is accurate, current and correct and will not impersonate or misrepresent any person or falsely misrepresent your affiliation with anyone or anything.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Type of Information</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When you access our service we processes some of your Device Information. Depending on how you access and use our service, we may receive:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Analytics and consumer information, log information, content consumption and queries you submit.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Device information such as the type of device you are using, your browser or operating system and your Internet Protocol address.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Geographic information including your device telemetry when you enable location based services.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Third party information such as identity verification services, financial services and social media.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Why we collect Information</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We collect information in order to identify you and to commercially transact with you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We process your data in order to fulfil any obligations to you when you order goods.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Communicate with you regarding our products or services, including billing, customer support, resolving complaints and quality control.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Notify you about changes to our services and products, terms and conditions, privacy policy or privacy notices, and any other changes that impact the quality of our service.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We send you promotional information about specials on products or services that may interest you, unless you have opted out of receiving promotional content.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ensure our compliance with any legal or regulatory statutes such as tax or financial laws.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Undertake research and statistics that do not include your Personal Information and cannot be linked to you or personally identify you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Data Retention</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We keep your Personal Information for as long as we need it to provide a service to you and uphold the contract between you and us.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We keep your Personal Information for as long it is required by law and is in line with our retention policy.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You hereby agree to us keeping your Personal Information subject to your request to stop processing your data.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We will retain your data for as long as is necessary to achieve the purpose for which it was collected or processed. If your data was used for more than one purpose, we will retain it until the last obligation expires.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Browser Tracking</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When you access our service we may use various methods to improve your experience through the use of browser cookies and tracking.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cookies are small text files placed on the device that you use and do not contain Personal Information but allow us to associate a user with a particular browser.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All websites use cookies to improve user experience, limit advertising, personalise interactions and tailor content to the user’s interests and ensuring device compatibility.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>By accessing our website you consent to the use of browser cookies.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Promotions</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You have the right to opt out from direct marketing and request us not to further contact you with promotions by any form of electronic communication such as email, SMS or instant messaging by “opting-out” of any communication we may send to you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>We do not sell your Personal Information to third parties for their marketing or any other purposes.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Access to Information</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We may make your data available to our employees, service providers and suppliers to enable us to deliver goods and services to you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Service providers that expedite business operations such as courier services, after sales and customer care departments are obligated to treat your data as confidential information and are authorised only to liaise directly with you regarding goods or services purchased and which may require their involvement.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In addition law enforcement agencies investigating fraud, or illegal activities may request access to our records and support with criminal investigations.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Location of Information</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our server infrastructure is located in different countries and we may transfer and host your data outside the geographic borders of your country for various purposes including for security, redundancy, data storage, back-ups and high availability of systems.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When we transfer your Personal Information, we will ensure that we do so in accordance with the requirements for lawful transfer as set out in the legislation of your country.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>By accessing our website you consent to the location of your Personal Information</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Information Security</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We secure the data in our possession or under our control by taking appropriate, reasonable technical and organisational measures to prevent loss of, damage to or unauthorised destruction or access to Personal Information.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In order to implement and maintain such security measures, we have in place policies, controls and related processes, which are reviewed and updated on a regular basis.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our policies, controls and procedures include physical, technical and network security, access controls and monitoring, secure storage, and encryption of Personal Information.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Should you disclose your Personal Information to any third party we shall not be liable for any loss or damage suffered by you, because such third party use of your data is beyond our control.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Right to Information</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Upon proof of identity you have the right to view and amend your Personal Information using your user account.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You may request to have your Personal Information corrected, destroyed or deleted.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Where requests to access to your Personal Information are excessive we may charge an administrative fee or refuse the request.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You can stop being a user by cancelling your account and by not accessing our website. Your Personal Information will only be kept subject to any legislative requirements.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As a registered user, you can exercise all your rights set out above.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This version of the Privacy Policy replaces any preceding privacy policy provisions on our website. We may occasionally update this Privacy Policy.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When you use our service the version of the Privacy Policy updated on this page applies to you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Lodging a Complaint</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Should you have any complaints about this Privacy Policy or our compliance you may contact us for a resolution or exercise your right to file a complaint with the Regulator in your country.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Privacy Policy','','publish','closed','closed','','privacy-policy','','','2021-11-25 10:39:39','2021-11-25 08:39:39','',0,'https://bluestar.herebetalent.com/?page_id=3',0,'page','',0),(4,1,'2021-11-24 17:01:55','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2021-11-24 17:01