these requirements could delay the processing of your request or result in its decline altogether.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Unwanted products</strong>&nbsp;(new and unopened)</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>You can return most new, unopened</strong>&nbsp;<strong>and unwanted products to us at no charge, provided:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1) It is&nbsp;undamaged and unused, with the original labels and stickers still attached;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2) Save in relation to Unboxed Deals it is in the&nbsp;original packaging.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>3) The packaging must be undamaged and in its original condition.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>4) The product is not missing any&nbsp;accessories or parts;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>5) You log a return within 7 days from the date upon which the courier delivered the products to you. You may have to bear the cost of return.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>6) After 30 days you can only return a product if it is defective and not one of the products listed below. We will exchange the returned product for another product of your choice or credit your&nbsp;<strong>subscriber</strong>&nbsp;account with the amount of the product you returned, which credit you may use in the future to purchase other products. Of course, if the exchanged product or the product you purchase later is more expensive than the product you returned, you will have to pay the difference. before we ship the exchanged or purchased product. You may have to bear the cost of delivery of the exchanged or purchased product to you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>7) Once we have validated your return, we will credit your subscriber account within 10 days of the return or refund you if that is your preference.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Keep in mind: Not all items are eligible for a pre-paid return. In this case, you will need to return the item at your own expense. We recommend you return the item(s) using a trackable method at the carrier of your choice.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Provisions</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Credit for returns on the following products is not possible:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Any product missing the serial number or UPC; Items with special shipping restrictions</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Electronic devices that has been unsealed and assembled;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Your selection of an incorrect size would not be a valid reason for return under the Act, so you should take care to check and confirm measurements before ordering.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Product which has been personalised for you or made to your specifications; due to personal configuration inscription or design on these products, unless the products are damaged/defective upon arrival, or materially different from what was ordered. If there is a misspelling or error in the configuration, inscription, or design due to a mistake by the seller, you are protected. All product packaging must be returned with the item. Products missing all their applicable tags are not acceptable for return.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Waterproof pet blankets and car seat covers that has been opened and assembled after delivery.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Exchanging a Product</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Certain products can be exchanged for a different size, colour or variation if available.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Unboxed deals,&nbsp;reconditioned products or used products can only be exchanged for a variation of the same product if such a variation is available.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We will exchange the returned product for another product of your choice or credit your&nbsp;subscriber account with the amount of the product you returned, which credit you may use in the future to purchase other products. Of course, if the exchanged product or the product you purchase later is more expensive than the product you returned, you will have to pay the difference before we ship the exchanged or purchased product. You will also have to bear the cost of delivery of the exchanged or purchased product to you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If such variation is not available, we will credit your account with the purchase price of the product within 10 days of the return or refund you if that is your preference.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are entitled to inspect all products and validate returns.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Wrong Product</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If we accidentally deliver the wrong product to you, or if the product is not as described on the Website, please notify us within 7 days and we will collect the product from you at no charge.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Once we have inspected the product and validated your return, we will at your choice deliver the correct product to you as soon as possible or credit your&nbsp;subscriber account with the purchase price of the product within 10 days of the return.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Damaged Product</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Should a product be damaged or missing any parts or accessories at the time of delivery or collection,&nbsp;please notify us within&nbsp;7 days by logging a return on the Website.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We will arrange to collect the product from you at no charge. Once we have inspected the product and validated your return, we will at your choice repair or replace the product or credit your&nbsp;subscriber account with the purchase price of the product or refund you if this is your preference.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Defective Products</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>We strive to deliver only high quality products without defects</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The following is not regarded as defects or valid returns:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1) Faults resulting from normal wear and tear;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2) Damage arising from negligence, user abuse or incorrect usage of the product;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>3) Damage arising from electrical surges or sea air corrosion;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>4) Damage arising from a failure to adequately care for the product;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>5) Damage arising from unauthorised alterations to the product;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>6) Where the product, although accurately described for its intended use, do not suit you;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>7) And in relation to Unboxed Deals or used products, signs of handling and or repackaging.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Standard Warranty</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you have received a defective product or of poor quality, please notify us as soon as reasonably possible, but in any event&nbsp;within 90 days after delivery except in the case of an extended supplier warranty.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Once logged on our Website, we will arrange to collect the product from you at no charge. Once we have inspected the product and validated your return, we will at your choice repair or replace the product or credit your&nbsp;subscriber account with the purchase price of the product or refund you if this is your preference.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Where there is no extended supplier warranty we cannot facilitate returns outside the 90 day period.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A product in perfectly new condition is not the same product as an Unboxed Deal,&nbsp;reconditioned product or used product. This is why Unboxed Deals,&nbsp;reconditioned products and used products are discounted, compared to products in perfectly new condition.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Supplier Warranty</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>A product may have a supplier warranty that extends beyond the 90 day Standard Warranty.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If such a product turns out to be defective after 90 days please notify us as soon as reasonably possible after you become aware of the defect, but in any event&nbsp;within the extended supplier warranty period<strong>&nbsp;</strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You can do so by logging a return on the Website, and we will facilitate your return of the product to the supplier at no charge. Unfortunately we cannot facilitate returns that fall outside of the supplier warranty period.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Please note that any extended supplier warranty is subject to whatever terms and conditions the supplier or manufacturer may impose. These are usually stated in a brochure or leaflet inside or on the product packaging. It is your responsibility to familiarise yourself of any such terms and conditions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It is also important to note that it will be in the supplier or manufacturer’s discretion what remedy it can offer you.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>We are under no obligation to provide you with a credit, repair or replacement, as the remedy lies with the supplier or manufacturer.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>PLEASE NOTE: Unboxed Deals, certain reconditioned products and used products do not have extended supplier warranties and this will be made clear on the product description page.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Direct Warranty</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A direct warranty is a product where the relevant manufacturer only deal directly with the customer, and not through us. Examples include electronic products.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If a direct warranty product turns out to be defective or otherwise of poor quality, please notify us and we will provide you with the relevant manufacturer’s contact details. Alternatively, you can notify the relevant manufacturer directly if you already have their details.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Other than this, the same limits and general principles of the standard warranty and extended supplier warranty apply to direct warranty products.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Charges and Refunds</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you return a defective product to us, but you fail to return all of the accessories and parts that were sold with that product, we are entitled to refuse acceptance,&nbsp; or to estimate the value of the missing accessories and parts and to credit or refund you in respect of the