:paragraph -->\n<p>Other than this, the same limits and general principles of the standard warranty and extended supplier warranty apply to direct warranty products.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Charges and Refunds</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you return a defective product to us, but you fail to return all of the accessories and parts that were sold with that product, we are entitled to refuse acceptance,&nbsp; or to estimate the value of the missing accessories and parts and to credit or refund you in respect of the returned product only.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you return a product that does not comply with this Policy, you may be liable to reimburse us for the cost of collecting the product from you and the cost of having the product returned to you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We regret that we do not refund the purchase price of non-faulty products that you return and will only exchange them for other products or credit your&nbsp;subscriber account. We also do not refund or credit delivery costs.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It can take up to 25 days for an item to reach the Distributor once you return it. Once the item is received at their fulfilment center, it takes 2 business days for the refund to be processed and 3-5 business days for the refund amount to show up in your account.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Refund And Return Policy','','inherit','closed','closed','','83-revision-v1','','','2021-11-25 10:39:06','2021-11-25 08:39:06','',83,'https://bluestar.herebetalent.com/?p=85',0,'revision','',0);
